description	"501st Clone Captain

^2Weaponry:
- DC-17 Blaster Pistol (2)
- DC-15A Clone Rifle (2)
-- 3 Concussive Rounds
-- 3 Ion Rounds
- PLX-1 (6 Rockets)
- 2 Thermal Detonators
- 3 Fire Grenades

^8Attributes:
- Blast Armour
- Stamina (2)
- Healing (1)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]

The Clone Captains were always to be seen leading their troops in the heart of the battlefield.  They generally had more advanced training and sometimes actual combat experience, so were well suited to handle the explosive munitions of their units."